title: Would you dare stay in room six?
text:
Would you dare stay in room six? Would you dare stay in room six? Next Story Prev Story 1 hr ago Read more: NEWS.com.au 
DARE to stay the night in Australia's oldest continuously licensed hotel and you might be completely freaked out by its hauntings. FEDERAL Group will put the handbrake on investment in Tasmania if it does not get certainty over a gaming licence in the state, says managing director Greg Farrell.   NEWS.com.au.
